peft_model_responses:
I'm sorry to hear that you're facing difficulties with your mortgage payments, but let's see what we can do here. Cancelling a mortgage is not as simple or straightforward as closing a credit card account, so our team will need some guidance from you regarding this specific situation.

To assist you further, please provide more information about how much money you currently owe on your mortgage (if available), any recent statements related to payment history, and if there have been any changes made recently due to unforeseen circumstances like job loss or medical expenses. This will allow us to better understand your financial status and explore possible solutions tailored specifically to your needs.

Rest assured, we'll work diligently to find alternative options until you receive satisfactory relief through other means such as refinancing or restructuring your loan terms. We appreciate your patience while exploring these possibilities together! If needed, feel free to reach out again at {{Customer Support Phone Number}} during business hours or via email at {{Customer Support Email Address}
